C4 concept: "like a"

sdr> /program = C4 ; setFormation(Formation.SQUARED_SET)
|      3Gv  3Bv
|
| 4B>            2G<
|
| 4G>            2B<
|
|      1B^  1G^
sdr> heads square thru
| 4B>  3G<  3B>  2G<
| 
| 4G>  1B<  1G>  2B<
sdr> /// like a hot foot spin == spin the top
sdr> like a hot foot spin
| 4G^  1Bv  4B^  3Gv  1G^  2Bv  3B^  2Gv
sdr> /// finish like a hot foot spin == fan the top
sdr> finish (like a hot foot spin)
| 4G>  1G>
| 
| 1B<  2B<
| 
| 4B>  3B>
| 
| 3G<  2G<
sdr> /// like a mix == centers trade
sdr> like a mix
| 4G>  1G>
| 
| 4B<  3B<
| 
| 1B>  2B>
| 
| 3G<  2G<
sdr> swing thru twice ; acey deucey
| 4G>  3G>
| 
| 4B<  3B<
| 
| 1B>  2B>
| 
| 1G<  2G<
sdr> right and left grand ; promenade home
|      3Gv  3Bv
| 
| 4B>            2G<
| 
| 4G>            2B<
| 
|      1B^  1G^
sdr> /exit
